title: Does Your Education Suck?

description:
Episode 630 - How much did you pay for your education? Was it worth it? What if I told you that right now there is a wealth of knowledge that will make you happier, more successful and more peaceful and it's either cheap or free? Well in this episode, I am going to dive into the topic of education. Follow me on Instagram at https://www.instagram.com/robdialjr/
